{
  "stem": "7094.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost my God on the way, so now I haven't got it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I am Jewish by culture, but religiously I've lost my God on the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, especially as my grandmother was in the last stages on the train with me, and I ask her, why are you here?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because she was really an extraordinary person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had the true religion, because she told me, God wishes like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to the last minute, she really believed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very religious people, good people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Religious people on the whole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps the young people were already influenced by new ideas, left-wing intellectual ideas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But most of the people that I'm extended, we mixed in, were very orthodox and religious.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you think that there are particular things that your family did as a Hasidic family, that-- I mean, are there things you can tell me that were specific and interesting?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there are many things that I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we always, when we had a simcha celebration, it was always communal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, again, shared with other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was never just a simcha for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told you that the weekly parcel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Any Jewish with the-- when there was a Jewish holiday, the parcels would include for Pesach, matzohs and wine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For Purim, other things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very-- she really dedicated her life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was very religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was praying three times a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was no committee, so it depended on two or three richer families, relatively, who took upon themselves to look after the poor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At one stage, she was going to have a new coat, a fur coat.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
